cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image classification and proposes a method to handle large resolution images. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a new principled variational lower bound to maximize the conditional classification likelihood. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with deep neural networks and their application to image classification. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also possible as the paper deals with deep neural networks and their optimization. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper deals with large resolution images taken by modern smartphone cameras and smart devices.
